<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Selecionar Pasta de Imagens</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Selecionar Pasta de Imagens</h1>
    <% if @error_message %>
      <p class="error"><%= @error_message %></p>
    <% end %>
    <p>Por favor, digite o caminho completo para a pasta que cont√©m suas imagens.</p>
    <form class="form-control" action="/" method="get">
      <input type="text" name="path" placeholder="/home/Pictures" required>
      <button type="submit">Carregar Imagens</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
